New Product Showcase    




 
This is your opportunity to obtain special press and publicity for 
            your new products in a highly visible and secure showroom location 
            adjacent to the trade show floor. 

To kick off this showcase, we have invited all of the media attendees 
            and independent specialty retailers to a special reception that 
            will be held in the New Product Showcase. The showcase will  
            be open to  buyers and media representatives only during regular show hours. 

Award of Distinction
The New Product Showcase Awards of Distinction is sponsored  by All Baby & Child, Corporation. 

              The Awards of Distinction recognize the best products from participating brands in each of the following nine categories: Apparel, Layette & Gift; Baby Care & Safety Products; Baby Gear: Furniture, Room Decor & Bedding; Maternity & Nursing Mom; Feeding, Training, Health & Nutrition; Toys and Games, Books & Audio/Visual & Baby Tech. Click here for more information.
Winners of the Awards of Distinction  will  be announced and their product displayed on the overhead screens at the All  Attendee Industry Reception being held on October 17, 2017. Each winner will  receive a glass trophy, certificate and ribbon.

