Option International NV - CloudGate Serial (RS-232) Expansion Card

TESSCO SKU :

510259

Mfg Part #:

CG1101-11919

Qty/UOM :

1
EACH

UPC:

5414140064634



The CG1101-11919 serial expansion module is for the Option CloudGate modem (TESSCO SKU: 519739 and 540260). The serial expansion module increases the connectivity of the CloudGate modem by allowing you to connect your serial device to the modem.The expansion module is easily installed by removing two Torx screws, and installing the Serial module. The Serial Module has a maximum speed of 921.6K baud.

